title: Fiddler on the Roof [Yiddish Version] Shmuel Rudenski as Tevye[F
description:
Yiddish version of Fiddler on the roof (A fidler afn dakh)

   1. Di Toyre (Tradition)
   2. Shadkhnte, Shadkhnte (Matchamker, Matchmaker)
   3. Ven ikh bin a rotshild (If I Were A Rich Man)
   4. Kaboles-Shabes Lid (Sabbath Prayer)
   5. Lekhayim (To Life)
   6. Nisim (Miracle of Miracles)
   7. Der Kholem (Tevye&#039;s Dream)
   8. Tog Ayn, Tog Oys (Sunrise, Sunset)
   9. Khasene Tants (Wedding Dance)
  10. Libst&#039; Mikh, Sertse? (Do you Love Me?)
  11. Vayt fun Mayn Liber Heym (Far From The Home I Love)
  12. Anatevka 

Shmuel Rudenski + Yiddish Cast
